data.description: Have you been looking for a home with massive land? Well you have found it? This 2010 double wide home features a ton of space inside with an open concept split floor plan. Upon entry into the home you are met with a large living space and large kitchen and dining room space. You will also find large guest rooms and master bedroom with massive bath. Inside of the master bath there is a large garden tub to relax in after a long day's work. Situated on nearly an acre of land, this is country living at its best! This is surely enough of room for all of your big boy toys! It's also minutes away from Lafayette and the Target Shopping Center. Location, location, location! Don't let this one pass you by!
